Outline for algorithm: 

1. Separate members from forbidden groupings into “partial groups”.
2. Create partial groups for mandatory groupings.
3. Create a score for every student by adding up GPA and skill ratings.
4. Sort students by score.
5. Divide the list into segments according to the size of the groups.
6. Finish off partial groups.
7. Take a student from each segment to make the rest of the balanced groups.
